Component Name      : PC_SPMedicalBenefitsInvestigation
Description         : This component is used for setting properties for Medical Benefits Investigation through BRE.
CreatedBy           : Deloitte
Created Date        : 25 March 2022
Modification Log    :
*****************************************************************************************************
Developer                   Date                   Description
********************************************************************************************
Chetna Mohapatra            25 Mar 2022           Initial version
*****************************************************************************************
